properties.Name: EquifaxCreditInquiryType
properties.Description:
The Equifax credit inquiry type.

Ex:

PRM - inquiries were given to a credit grantor to provide a firm offer of credit or insurance.    It remains for 12 months.

AM or AR = inquiries indicated a periodic review of credit history by a creditor.

EMPL = inquiry related to an employment inquiry.

EFX = inquiries indicates an Equifax activity in response to a contact for a copy of credit file.

NO = inquiry that do not display to credit grantors.

No MR = inquiries that indicate the reissue of a mortgage credit report in connection with a mortgage loan.

PR = inquiry indicates that a creditor reviewed your account as part of a portfolio they are purchasing.

Properties.Description:
The Equifax credit inquiry type.

Ex:

PRM - inquiries were given to a credit grantor to provide a firm offer of credit or insurance.    It remains for 12 months.

AM or AR = inquiries indicated a periodic review of credit history by a creditor.

EMPL = inquiry related to an employment inquiry.

EFX = inquiries indicates an Equifax activity in response to a contact for a copy of credit file.

NO = inquiry that do not display to credit grantors.

No MR = inquiries that indicate the reissue of a mortgage credit report in connection with a mortgage loan.

PR = inquiry indicates that a creditor reviewed your account as part of a portfolio they are purchasing.
